## Project Overview

This is a **Uniweb** project - a component web platform that separates content from code.

{{#if isMulti}}
```
{{projectName}}/
├── foundations/        # Shared component libraries
│   └── default/        # Default foundation
├── sites/              # Content sites
│   └── main/           # Main site
├── package.json        # Root workspace config
└── pnpm-workspace.yaml
```
{{else}}
```
{{projectName}}/
├── foundation/     # React component library (code)
├── site/           # Content and pages (markdown)
├── package.json    # Root workspace config
└── pnpm-workspace.yaml
```
{{/if}}

### Foundation vs Site

- **Foundation**: A React component library. Components with `meta.js` are **exposed** to content authors.
- **Site**: Content written in markdown. The runtime loads the foundation and renders content.
